high_descs: Turn to your left, and look at the tub
Pick up the sponge that's on the floor of the tub
Turn to your right and go over to the sink
Place the sponge into the sink and rinse it off then pick it back up
Take the sponge back to the tub
Place the sponge onto the floor of the tub, near the bottom middle
anns.task_desc: Place a newly rinsed off sponge into the tub

high_descs: Turn around walk to the tub
Grab the green sponge from the tub
Turn right, walk to the sink
Put the sponge in the sink, turn on the faucet, wash the sponge, turn off the faucet, take the sponge out
Turn around, walk back to the tub
Put the green sponge back in the tub
anns.task_desc: Wash the green sponge from the tub, put it back

high_descs: Pick up the sponge from the tub.
Bring the sponge to the sink.
Wet the sponge with water in the sink.
Bring the sponge to the tub.
Put the wet sponge in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet sponge in the tub.
